                    span.title Diabetes
                    .description Improved circulation, lower blood sugar levels, and a higher metabolism are some of the benefits of walk-in tubs for diabetes patients.
            li
                .icon-wrap
                    img.preview.lazyload.preloader(data-src="./static/images/common/improve-health/Therapy.png", alt="Therapy")       
                .item-body
                    span.title Therapy
